{"tid":358314,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 我懷疑男朋友屋企有鬼","createTime":"2017-08-13T15:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T18:08:46.000Z","uid":136444,"like":9,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d03e7c381bcecd58cb1ecc8945d271e765ee6e2","tid":358314,"uid":136444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:48:35.000Z","msg":"是咁的，男朋友屋企今晚冇人，就諗住放工之後上去hea下，過下二人世界咁，咁原本就諗住我放工之後就買餸上去玩下煮飯仔，食完飯一齊睇碟啦。<br />\n<br />\n點知老細話有個同事要調更，所以可以早啲收工，咁早左收工冇同男朋友講，諗住買埋餸再上佢屋企比個驚喜佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我買完餸就上去啦，去到門口就㩒佢鐘，但我男朋友好耐都未開門，於是就㩒多幾下，佢終於都嚟開門，不過就冇著上身衫，得條毛巾遮住個下身，原來佢準備去沖涼，點知我突然上嚟佢唔知所以先咁衝忙。咁我就叫佢快啲去沖涼，我就去準備下啲食材先啦。<br />\n<br />\n咁正當我洗菜嘅時候，突然聽到佢間房好似有啲聲，咁我初初都冇為意。點知隔左一陣有打乞痴嘅聲從我男朋友間房傳出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要連續幾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 於是我就行入去諗住睇下啦，入到佢房，發現啲聲係由衣櫃傳出嚟，正當我想打開個衣櫃嚟睇下嘅時候，竟然有撞到衣櫃門嘅聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我男朋友突然走左出嚟叫停我，我問點解唔可以開，佢就話頭先執緊野放到啲野好亂，驚一開跌晒啲野出嚟，叫我出去廳度等佢，出廳嘅時候見到房門後面地下有件女人衫，咁平時佢呀媽都有借佢衣櫃嘅一格嚟擺衫嘅，咁所以當晚就信佢應該真係執緊衣櫃。<br />\n<br />\n咁我一直坐喺廳等到男朋友出嚟嘅時候，佢就話今晚不如都係出去食野，佢個樣仲要好驚青咁，直到我地出左去，佢先至好似安樂晒咁。<br />\n<br />\n我問佢咩事佢一直都唔講，佢話就話執衣櫃，但我覺得佢講緊大話，我越諗就越覺得佢屋企有鬼，仲住喺佢衣櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請問各位巴絲打有冇作法驅鬼嗰啲好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed48fc23f4034adcdef7e27f25c6b0be6e16e065","tid":358314,"uid":131836,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"難分真與假"},{"pid":"007113b89f690754ac7812f29a056e89968e1789","tid":358314,"uid":88944,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:51:10.000Z","msg":"0分重作"},{"pid":"52ec800df91dd512edce467f428ca4c3f2cbf5d9","tid":358314,"uid":704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:51:15.000Z","msg":"帽"},{"pid":"7da322919365efd16fc1f16aae1ed302469da5b8","tid":358314,"uid":21980,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:51:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">護眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"86edc44f353978a8337fe24df104ee602bee45a0","tid":358314,"uid":36238,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:51:52.000Z","msg":"2/10 毫無驚喜 勇氣可嘉"},{"pid":"4e11b2bdbfbdafa18de8427e9a021ade8b3d967c","tid":358314,"uid":136444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>難分真與假</blockquote><br />\n我好認真架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212f81b547dffb079f79505fa4dd77435731681f","tid":358314,"uid":136444,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:55:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帽</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩帽？可以驅鬼？"},{"pid":"16b0d49b878710f98a24e45d58fc3e500d6ee5d2","tid":358314,"uid":52903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:56:45.000Z","msg":"多謝分享"},{"pid":"28ed251eb65860c0b9fc224e55737bfe6c90aac8","tid":358314,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:56:53.000Z","msg":"第二條女黎"},{"pid":"3ac1f44516fc9f94e8f8ef25df8a0a9b59601208","tid":358314,"uid":6337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:57:32.000Z","msg":"有啲野冇得勉強"},{"pid":"eb01164f514d93004f0e6e58230438f9e6501f15","tid":358314,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:59:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>帽</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩帽？可以驅鬼？</blockquote><br />\n佢想講(帽事 唔洗驚)姐"},{"pid":"d01d2b9c2a7688f440bb25c48ad143b63d16b02d","tid":358314,"uid":136444,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"